### 보드 ID 검색
GET {{domain}}/board/id/{{boardId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### 보드 사용자 ID 검색
GET {{domain}}/board/project/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### 보드 추가
POST {{domain}}/board
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
    "projectId": {{projectId}},
    "name": "철수 보드",
    "orderNo": 3
}

### 보드 수정
PATCH {{domain}}/board
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "id": {{boardId}},
  "name": "영희 보드"
}

### 보드 순서 수정
PATCH {{domain}}/board/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

[
  { "id": 42, "orderNo": 0 },
  { "id": 43, "orderNo": 1 },
  { "id": 44, "orderNo": 2 },
  { "id": 45, "orderNo": 3 }
]

### 보드 삭제
DELETE {{domain}}/board
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "id": {{boardId}}
}